  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Thread sausage, zucchini, onion, and bell pepper onto skewers.",
    "3. Brush skewers with sesame oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "4. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until sausage is cooked through.",
    "5. If desired, brush with soy sauce and honey during the last minute of grilling.",
    "6. Serve skewers hot, garnished with sesame seeds and sliced green onions if desired.",
    "7. Serve with cozy on the side, if desired."
